Tue Mar 31 20:12:53 UTC 2026 - Mia Herkt <mia@0x0.st>

- Avoid binfmt_misc registration in sciptlets
  There are transfiletriggers for binfmt.d installed by the
  systemd package, so this package should not do that.
  Additionally, this would cause package install to fail in
  environments with restricted permissions if it happens to get
  pulled in as a dependency.

